OL,3,CWho is Ian Paterson the butcher
OL,4,Csurgeon and what did he do?
OL,6,FAn ITV documentary, Bodies of
OL,7,FEvidence: The Butcher Surgeon,
OL,8,Funcovers the shocking story of Ian
OL,9,FPaterson and his victims.
OL,11,FPaterson, who was based in Birmingham,
OL,12,Fis currently serving a 20-year
OL,13,Fsentence for his crimes, after
OL,14,Fcarrying out needless operations over
OL,15,Fa 14-year period.
OL,17,FWhile working as a breast surgeon
OL,18,Fconsultant, he was diagnosing cancer
OL,19,Fwhen there wasn't any and cutting
OL,20,Fpatients open for no reason.
