OL,3,CWho is Ian Paterson the butcher
OL,4,Csurgeon and what did he do?
OL,6,FHe was found guilty in 2017 of 17
OL,7,Fcounts of wounding with intent and
OL,8,Fthree counts of unlawful wounding.
OL,10,FFive years on, this film from the ITV
OL,11,FExposure strand talks to victims,
OL,12,Ffellow doctors and a key whistleblower
OL,13,Fto tell the extraordinary story of how
OL,14,Fthe system allowed Paterson to perform
OL,15,Funnecessary and damaging surgery on so
OL,16,Fmany for so long.
OL,18,FHere's a guide to who Ian Paterson is
OL,19,Fand how he performed damaging
OL,20,Fsurgeries:
