OL,6,FWho is Ian Paterson?
OL,8,FThe breast surgeon, 62, is currently
OL,9,Fserving 20 years for his 14-year
OL,10,Fcampaign of botched operations he
OL,11,Fcarried out in the West Midlands.
OL,13,FPaterson, who is due to be freed in
OL,14,F2027, was jailed in 2017 for wounding
OL,15,Fwith intent and unlawfully wounding
OL,16,Fnine women and one man he treated
OL,17,Fbetween 1997 and 2011.
