OL,6,FWhen was Ian Paterson suspended?
OL,8,FIan Paterson was not suspended from
OL,9,Fcarrying out his NHS or private work
OL,10,Funtil 2011. Whistleblowers said they
OL,11,Freported concerns about Paterson years
OL,12,Fbefore this.
OL,14,FWhat is the Paterson inquiry?
OL,16,FThe Paterson inquiry investigated how
OL,17,Fthe surgeon was able to carry out
OL,18,Funnecessary surgeries undetected for
OL,19,Fso many years.
