OL,6,FIn 2020 it found "patients were let
OL,7,Fdown over many years" by the NHS and
OL,8,Fprivate hospitals and opportunities to
OL,9,Fstop Paterson were "missed, time after
OL,10,Ftime".
OL,12,FInquiry chairman the Rt Rev Graham
OL,13,FJames, Bishop of Norwich, said there
OL,14,Fwas a culture of "avoidance and
OL,15,Fdenial", which allowed the breast
OL,16,Fsurgeon to carry out unnecessary and
OL,17,Fbotched operations on hundreds of
OL,18,Fwomen.
