OL,3,CWho is Ian Paterson the butcher
OL,4,Csurgeon and what did he do?
OL,6,FThe inquiry recommended the NHS Trust
OL,7,Fwhich employed Paterson and private
OL,8,Fhealth firm Spire Healthcare recall
OL,9,Fall of Paterson's patients.
OL,11,FHow many victims did Ian Paterson have?
OL,13,FA total of 675 out of 1,207 women who
OL,14,Funderwent the unregulated treatment
OL,15,Fhad died by 2017.
OL,17,FMore than 750 victims have already
OL,18,Fsuccessfully claimed after receiving
OL,19,Funapproved and life-threatening
OL,20,Fsurgery from Paterson - who treated
OL,21,Fmore than 11,000 patients.
