OL,6,FWhat has happened at the inquests into
OL,7,Fthe deaths of his patients ?
OL,9,FIan Paterson has so far refused to
OL,10,Fattend the first of more than 60
OL,11,Finquests touching on the deaths of his
OL,12,Fformer patients because he believes
OL,13,Fthe coroner's investigation is
OL,14,F"biased", the court has been told.
OL,16,FThe breast surgeon was ordered by
OL,17,Fcoroner Richard Foster to appear
OL,18,Fremotely at Birmingham and Solihull
OL,19,FCoroner's Court to give evidence at
OL,20,Fthe inquest of Chloe Nikitas, who died
OL,21,Fat the age of 43 in April 2008.
