OL,6,FMr Foster issued a ruling on the 21st
OL,7,FOctober saying he could "find no
OL,8,Freason" why Paterson could not attend
OL,9,Fthe inquest and give evidence remotely
OL,10,Ffrom prison, and said it was
OL,11,F"disappointing" to the families of the
OL,12,Fvictims that he had decided not to
OL,13,Fappear.
