OL,6,FPaterson had been accused of
OL,7,Fattempting to delay the hearings after
OL,8,Flodging an application to have his
OL,9,Fwitness summons revoked the day before
OL,10,Fthe first inquest was due to start on
OL,11,FOctober 10, citing health concerns, a
OL,12,Flack of legal representation and
OL,13,F"inadequate facilities to prepare".
OL,15,FThe first inquest into the death of
OL,16,Fone of Paterson's patients heard on
OL,17,Fthe 22nd October that a mother who was
OL,18,Fgiven a "cleavage-sparing" mastectomy
OL,19,Fthen had her breast cancer return.
