OL,3,CWho is Ian Paterson the butcher
OL,4,Csurgeon and what did he do?
OL,6,FChloe Nikitas, an environmental
OL,7,Fconsultant from Tamworth, was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer in 2002
OL,9,Fand was treated by the West Midlands
OL,10,F"butcher" surgeon.
OL,12,FHe told her he could perform a
OL,13,Fmastectomy which would leave some skin
OL,14,Fbehind to ensure her cleavage would
OL,15,Flook normal.
OL,17,FShe then discovered a lump in the same
OL,18,Fbreast in 2005, which was the same
OL,19,Ftype of cancer she had three years
OL,20,Fearlier.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/15
